Callington is a small size town for shopping. It has four shopping streets {Fore Street, Church Street, Well {Street}and{New Road. Fore Street}is the main street.
{Acknowledgements:} The following have helped compile material for The Domesday Project:-{Mr. Peter Crumpler & his class of 9-11 year olds.{Ms. Kit {Marks}& her class of 7-9 year olds. {Nathaniel Wilson,}a pupil of Callington Comprehensive school, who taught children to type in text & data & who edited and refined much of the data. {Members of staff, parents and {H.M.I.s}who accompanied children of fieldtrips around the D-Block. July 1985
